data.description: Welcome home to 15700 Loblolly Ln, an immaculate 3 bedroom 3 bathroom oasis on a sprawling 1.73 acre lot. Located in Wyndemere, a private and serene lake-front community with lake access, tennis courts and basketball courts. You’re greeted with a huge foyer connecting you to the entire home. The giant kitchen with extensive storage and tons of natural light is going to be perfect for entertaining family this holiday season! The primary suite on the main level boasts huge closets and a new spa-like bathroom with marble tile and high-end fixtures. An extra wide stairway leads you to the basement, the entertainment space of this home. The large recreation room is full of natural light and an amazing dry-bar perfect for entertaining. An additional bedroom, bathroom and tool room with outside access for your lawn mower are found in the basement. An expansive poured concrete patio spans the back length of the home and is connected around both sides of the property. The large deck boasts 2 screened in porches and 1 screened in entertainment space below with an additional dry-bar. Water filtration system added in 2020. Primary suite bathroom renovation in 2020. Outdoor AC unit replaced in 2022. Updated Trex decking in 2023. Updated Samsung kitchen appliance package in 2023. Added vinyl under-roofing and gutters below the deck in 2023. Thanks for showing!
